 "<p>Assign a label for the attachment. It is useful to include the type of file. Eg. pdf, ppt, etc.<\/p><p>Including the size is also recommended so that after your package is exported to a web site, people will have an idea how long it would take to download this attachment.<\/p><p>For example: <code>Sales Forecast.doc (500kb)<\/code><\/p>": "<p>Tilf\u00f8j en m\u00e6rkat p\u00e5 det vedh\u00e6ftede. Det er en god id\u00e9 at inkludere filtype. Fx.: pdf, ppt, etc.<\/p><p>Det anbefales ogs\u00e5 at inkludere filst\u00f8relsen s\u00e5, at n\u00e5r din pakke eksporteres til en web site, s\u00e5 har man en id\u00e9 om, hvor lang tid det tager at overf\u00f8re det vedh\u00e6ftede .<\/p><p>For eksempel: <code>Salgsprognose.doc (500kb)<\/code><\/p>", 
